---
title: Smart Bacon and Roasted Sweet Potato Salad with Maple-Shallot Vinaigrette and Feta
description: As if maple syrup, smoky bacon, crisp apples and tender, roasted squash weren't enough, shallots do double flavour duty as a tart element and as a base for this balanced vinaigrette. This recipe is a real dinner no-brainer!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-de-patates-douces-roties-et-de-bacon-1e8f6221.jpg
